        "body": "### Checklist\n\n- [X] I made sure that there are *no existing issues* - [open](https://github.com/TeamNewPipe/NewPipe/issues) or [closed](https://github.com/TeamNewPipe/NewPipe/issues?q=is%3Aissue+is%3Aclosed) - which I could contribute my information to.\n- [X] I have read the [FAQ](https://newpipe.net/FAQ/) and my problem isn't listed.\n- [X] I'm aware that this is a request for NewPipe itself and that requests for adding a new service need to be made at [NewPipeExtractor](https://github.com/TeamNewPipe/NewPipeExtractor/issues).\n- [X] I have taken the time to fill in all the required details. I understand that the feature request will be dismissed otherwise.\n- [X] This issue contains only one feature request.\n- [X] I have read and understood the [contribution guidelines](https://github.com/TeamNewPipe/NewPipe/blob/dev/.github/CONTRIBUTING.md).\n\n### Feature description\n\nPlease a \"Live\" access tab on NewPipe as it is on youtube. This gives access to more videos from a channel.\n\n### Why do you want this feature?\n\n**Access to \"Live\" video tab as YouTube.**\r\n\r\nThis is about accessing more videos from a youtube channel that has a live tab.\r\n\r\n**What do you mean**\r\nI will illustrate this with a particular channel on YouTube. \r\n\r\nIt could be any channel that has a live channel.\r\n\r\nFirst when I am at a particular YouTube channel, I have the channel with videos.\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"videos\" src=\"https://github.com/TeamNewPipe/NewPipe/assets/26536316/60e1104c-a411-4506-accc-659bc361755f\" width=263 />\r\n\r\nNotice that there is a \"Videos\" tab. There is also a \"Live\" tab which gives you access to more videos.\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"live\" src=\"https://github.com/TeamNewPipe/NewPipe/assets/26536316/346d7184-5a50-4a8b-8e49-09192dab4027\" width=263 />\r\n\r\n**But Newpipe only has access to videos tab**\r\n<img alt=\"vodeos on newpipe\" src=\"https://github.com/TeamNewPipe/NewPipe/assets/26536316/2112df9d-bfa2-4896-a44e-cc5a1e82e7bc\" width=263 />\r\n\r\nThere is no \"Live\" tab to get access to additional videos as in Youtube.\r\n\r\n**What is the work around to access videos under the \"Live\" tab under NewPipe?**\r\n1. Goto the particular YouTube channel and select the video you like to watch and download on NewPipe.\r\n2. In the particular video under the \"Live\" tab click \"share\" and copy address to clipboard.\r\n3. Goto NewPipe. Click \"search\" and paste in NewPipe's search bar from clipboard the address you copied from the YouTube channel.\r\n4. Download the video from NewPipe\r\n\r\n**Therefore**\r\nAdding a \"Live\" button in NewPipe allows access to more videos that are only available in YouTube. \r\n\r\nIt saves having to use the \"work around\" described.\r\n\r\nThank you\r\nAnthony, Sydney\r\n\n\n### Additional information\n\n_No response_",
